# Cling ignore rules for your Home folder. "#" lines are comments.
# "#:group id=… name=…" headers mark a block of rules so a future settings UI
# can toggle whole groups. Rules you add yourself land under "#:custom" at the end.
# Syntax is gitignore: a trailing "/" matches directories, "!" re-includes.

